      <p>
        This website may contain links to external websites. The respective providers are responsible
        for their own content. External links are reviewed when added; ongoing monitoring without
        specific indication of unlawful content is not reasonable.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Copyright</h2>
      <p>
        Texts, images, layouts, and other content on this website are protected by copyright unless
        otherwise indicated. Use beyond statutory permissions requires prior written consent.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
